detail.name: Son Goten
detail.effect: [When Attacking] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand. Then, if you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 2 or less and return it to its owner's hand.

detail.name: 孫悟天
detail.effect: [アタック時]自分のライフ1枚までを手札に加える。その後、自分の手札が7枚以下の場合、相手のコスト2以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、手札に戻す。

faq.question: If this card's [When Attacking] skill increases your hand to 8 cards when you add a card from your life, does the "then, if you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 2 or less and return it to its owner's hand" skill apply?
このカードの【アタック時】でライフを加え手札が８枚になった場合、「その後、自分の手札が７枚以下の場合、相手のコスト２以下のバトルカード１枚までを選び、手札に戻す」部分のスキルを使えますか？
